data.description: Built in 2022, this manufactured home features a modern look, open floor plan, large kitchen island and vinyl flooring throughout. This home sits on a Bull Shoals frontage lot that includes an insulated 18x24 man cave/she shed. The shed includes a loft for storage, electric, and heating and cooling.  Love the lake? Beaver Creek Marina and public boat launch is just down the street.
